'''Q.2
Write a Python program that assigns values to four variables
 (integer, string, float, and boolean) in a single line and prints them.'''

a,b,c,d = 4,"Str",5.6,True

print(a)
print(b)
print(c)
print(d)

'''Output
4
Str
5.6
True'''

'''Q.3
